Trusted by lawyers, accountants, and business owners who need clarity, accuracy, and results." }, { icon: BuildingOfficeIcon, title: "Built to Hold Up — In Court, in Negotiation, in Strategy", description: "From legal disputes to boardroom decisions, our valuations are independent, logical, and confidently defendable. We've stood by them as expert witnesses." }, { icon: CurrencyDollarIcon, title: "More Than Valuers — Business Sales Experts", description: "With deep experience in selling businesses, we bring live market understanding — not static theory — to every valuation." }, { icon: AcademicCapIcon, title: "Academic Knowledge + Real-World Business Experience", description: "You benefit from a team that blends CPAs, Chartered Accountants, MBAs, economists, registered business valuers, and M&A professionals — combining technical precision with practical insight from real business sales." }, { icon: GlobeAltIcon, title: "Australia-Wide Reach, Specialist Insight", description: "You benefit from a team of 8 in-house valuers across the country, each with specialist knowledge in diverse industries and niches." } ]; const services = [ "Legal Proceedings & Disputes", "Succession Planning", "Exit Strategy", "Tax Purposes", "Mergers & Acquisitions", "Family Law Matters", "Insolvency & Bankruptcy", "Insurance Valuations", "Financial Reporting", "Expert Witness Services" ]; const testimonials = [ { name: "Michael and Karen Mazzarella", location: "Sutherland", text: "The valuer was genuine, friendly and very professional. They arranged a valuation of our business quickly and was flexible to our time schedule. The final report is better than we expected.", image: "/images/129 Xclussive Business Sales Headshots Newcastle Feb 2022_ Noni Carroll Photography.jpg" }, { name: "Chris Sarris", location: "Hunters Hill", text: "Thank you for the valuation of our business. Their knowledge around market trends really helped us to understand the final valuation.", image: "/images/57 Zoran Sarabaca-Xcllusive Headshots Mar 2021_Noni Carroll Photography.jpg" } ]; const teamMembers = [ { name: "Zoran Sarabaca", // role: "Senior Business Valuer", image: "/images/57 Zoran Sarabaca-Xcllusive Headshots Mar 2021_Noni Carroll Photography.jpg", description: "Expert in business valuations with over 15 years of experience in M&A and corporate finance." }, { name: "Business Valuation Experts", // role: "Lead Valuer", image: "/images/129 Xclussive Business Sales Headshots Newcastle Feb 2022_ Noni Carroll Photography.jpg", description: "Specialist in legal proceedings and dispute resolution valuations." }, { name: "Senior Consultant", role: "Business Sales Specialist", image: "/images/152 Xclussive Headshots Newcastle Feb 2022_ Noni Carroll Photography.jpg", description: "Focused on exit strategies and succession planning for business owners." } ]; const officePhotos = [ "/images/xclusive-office-visit-35.jpg", "/images/xclusive-office-visit-67.jpg", "/images/xclusive-office-visit-71.jpg", "/images/xclusive-office-visit-77.jpg", "/images/xclusive-office-visit-94.jpg", "/images/xclusive-office-visit-96.jpg" ]; return (
